headline: Ulta Beauty Teams up with Beyoncé’s COWBOY CARTER TOUR to Deliver the Ultimate Concert-Ready Beauty Experience
summary: BOLINGBROOK, Ill., April 24, 2025--Ulta Beauty, the nation’s largest beauty retailer, is proud to be the official beauty retail partner of Beyoncé’s COWBOY CARTER TOUR.
